'''Google新聞實驗室'''（Google News Lab）又稱'''谷歌新闻实验室'''，是[[Google|Google]]下設的一个全球性的团队，其目的是 "与记者和企业家合作，帮助媒体打造未来"<ref>{{Cite web|title=Introducing the News Lab|url=https://blog.google/outreach-initiatives/google-news-initiative/introducing-news-lab/|accessdate=|author=Grove|date=June 22, 2015|first=Steve|work=The Keyword|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225132330/https://blog.google/outreach-initiatives/google-news-initiative/introducing-news-lab/|archivedate=2021-02-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新闻实验室于2015年启动，該團隊与新闻机构合作，帮助和推动他們创新，应对行业挑战，并提供培训和新兴技术，使新聞機構將這些技術用于新聞报道<ref name="CJR">{{Cite news|url=https://www.cjr.org/the_media_today/google-news-initiative.php|title=The media today: Google offers news business a $300 million olive branch|author=Ingram|first=Mathew|date=March 21, 2018|accessdate=25 November 2018|agency=[[Columbia_Journalism_Review|Columbia Journalism Review]]|archive-date=2021-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210526213725/https://www.cjr.org/the_media_today/google-news-initiative.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年，Google新闻倡议（ Google News Initiative ）推出後，Google新聞實驗室被納入該項目<ref>{{Cite news|author=Wang|first=Shan|title=Google announces a $300M 'Google News Initiative' (though this isn't about giving out grants directly to newsrooms, like it does in Europe)|url=http://www.niemanlab.org/2018/03/google-announces-a-300m-google-news-initiative-though-this-isnt-about-giving-out-grants-directly-to-newsrooms-like-it-does-in-europe/|accessdate=25 November 2018|agency=Nieman Lab|publisher=Harvard University|date=March 20, 2018|archive-date=2021-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603152138/https://www.niemanlab.org/2018/03/google-announces-a-300m-google-news-initiative-though-this-isnt-about-giving-out-grants-directly-to-newsrooms-like-it-does-in-europe/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

